2024-06-28 16:36:44 - StudioAtrium\Entity\Project\Files\Download:Insert {"timestamp":1719592604,"user_id":16902,"user_ip":"109.173.156.166","user_browser":"Mozilla\/5.0 (Linux; Android 10; K) AppleWebKit\/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome\/126.0.0.0 Mobile Safari\/537.36","dao_classname":"StudioAtrium\\Entity\\Project\\Files\\Download\\DAO\\PDOMySQL","dao_event":"dao_object_insert","entity_classname":"StudioAtrium\\Entity\\Project\\Files\\Download","entity_data":{"id":21622,"__foreign_props":[],"project_id":"1431","file_type":"sketch","user_id":16902,"name":"Piotr","surname":"Lemke","email":"piotr.lemke@gmail.com","phone":"663601451","project_order_date":"2","create_date":"2024-06-28 16:36:44","status":"new","props":{"uwagi":"Prosz\u0119 o przes\u0142anie rysunk\u00f3w i aktualnego kosztorysu na adres piotr.lemke@gmail.com. \r\nCzy \u015bwiadcz\u0105 pa\u0144stwo us\u0142ugi adaptacyjne? Je\u017celi tak to prosz\u0119 o orientacyjny cennik. Je\u017celi nie to czy mog\u0105 pa\u0144stwo poleci\u0107 architekta z okolic Poznania?"},"attachments":[],"_uid":5535284},"entity_changes":false}
2024-06-28 16:41:45 - StudioAtrium\Entity\User\Message:Insert {"timestamp":1719592905,"user_id":16953,"user_ip":"109.241.47.50","user_browser":"Mozilla\/5.0 (Linux; Android 10; K) AppleWebKit\/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome\/126.0.0.0 Mobile Safari\/537.36","dao_classname":"StudioAtrium\\Entity\\User\\Message\\DAO\\PDOMySQL","dao_event":"dao_object_insert","entity_classname":"StudioAtrium\\Entity\\User\\Message","entity_data":{"id":1250,"__foreign_props":[],"user_id":16953,"parent_id":0,"author":"Krzysztof","title":"Zapytanie o projekt Ibis II Sz","message":"Dzie\u0144 dobry,\r\nRazem z \u017con\u0105 jeste\u015bmy zainteresowani projekt Ibis II. Jednak\u017ce ostatnio zauwa\u017cyli\u015bmy ten sam projekt w wersji sz ale niestety nasza dzia\u0142ka ma szeroko\u015b\u0107 delikatnie ponad 20 metr\u00f3w, dlatego chcia\u0142bym si\u0119 dopyta\u0107 dlaczego minimalna szeroko\u015b\u0107 dzia\u0142ki musi by\u0107 22,95m skoro szeroko\u015b\u0107 domu wynosi 10,95m.\r\nDodatkowo chcia\u0142bym podpyta\u0107 o mo\u017cliwo\u015b\u0107 zmiany w projekcie, a mianowicie do\u0142o\u017cenie ma\u0142ej spi\u017carni w kuchni jako osobne pomieszczenie. Czy istnieje taka mo\u017cliwo\u015b\u0107 i jaki by\u0142by koszt.\r\nDom murowany z pomp\u0105 ciep\u0142a.\r\nB\u0119d\u0119 bardzo wdzi\u0119czny za odpowied\u017a.\r\n\r\nPozdrawiam \r\nKrzysztof Klekociuk","create_date":"2024-06-28 16:41:45","status":"new","project_id":"1540","attachments":[],"_uid":320036},"entity_changes":false}
